          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052488/Etnomusicologisch Centrum</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指烏干達特索地區（Teso）和肯亞的拱形豎琴，具極細長的琴身及五至六根琴弦。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
